name: Antarctic Krill Oil 500mg Omega 3 Fatty Acid Supplement, MegaRed Extra Strength EPA & DHA Softgels (90cnt box), Antioxidant Astaxanthin, Heart Health Supplement With No Fish Oil Aftertaste
feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: Krill is one of the world’s most abundant and sustainable organisms. MegaRed only sources krill from the Antarctic where krill is most abundant.,OMEGA 3 SUPPLEMENT: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil has been shown to significantly increase your omega 3 index in just 30 days. Supportive research has shown that consumption of EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids may reduce the risk of coronary heart disease.,HEART HEALTH: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil supplements provide an optimal combination of omega-3 fatty acids and the powerful antioxidant astaxanthin to support heart health in a once daily softgel.,3X MORE PURE: MegaRed with PureTechTM is 3x MORE PURE than regular krill oil. Salts and other impurities are removed to provide the purest krill oil on the market.,NO FISHY AFTERTASTE and EASY ABSORPTION: Krill Oil is carried in a phospholipid form which is better absorbed by the human body and because it's krill oil as opposed to fish oil, MegaRed Krill Oil has no fishy aftertaste or odor.,These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.

feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL, RICH IN OMEGA-3s: BioEmblem's premium krill oil is sustainably harvested from the pristine waters of the Antarctic Ocean. Each 1000mg serving delivers 340mg of essential omega-3 fatty acids, 136mg of EPA, 64mg of DHA, along with phospholipids and astaxanthin.,SUPERIOR ABSORPTION FORM: Krill oil's phospholipid form of omega-3s can dissolve in water, allowing it to be better absorbed and more bioavailable compared to fish oils' triglycerides.* Krill oil also avoids the fishy aftertaste and odor associated with fish oils.,SUPPORTS HEALTHY BRAIN, HEART, AND JOINT HEALTH: The omega-3s (DHA and EPA) and astaxanthin found in krill oil have antioxidant properties and help maintain healthy cognitive function, promote cardiovascular health, and support healthy joints and mobility.*,EXTRA PURE, TESTED FOR HEAVY METALS: Our formula is filtered and tested for heavy metals and other contaminants. Every softgel is non-GMO, gluten free, soy free, dairy free, and corn free. There are no artificial ingredients, stearates, or sulfates.,BIOEMBLEM : BioEmblem Krill Oil is sourced from Antarctica and bottled in the USA at an NSF-registered, cGMP-certified facility in California.

Our fish oil omega 3 is delivered in triglyceride form, which is a better-absorbed form of omega 3 fatty acids.,✔️ IFOS 5-Star Certified - Our fish are wild caught using sustainable fishing practices – never farm raised. Plus, we use a combination of small fish (like sardines and mackerel), known to have less mercury and fewer toxins than bigger fish like salmon. Each batch is rigorously tested for purity and IFOS 5-Star Certified, a ranking system for premium quality fish oil.

This explains its near perfect absorption and utilization.,95% ABSORPTION RATE, 4.5 TIMES MORE EFFECTIVE THAN FISH OIL: In clinical testing free fatty acid omega 3 EPA & DHA were shown to have 4.5X higher absorption that standard fish oil* with an overall absorption rate of 95%. Making it the most effective form of Omega 3 available.,NO RANCID OILS, FISH OIL BURPS, or STOMACH DISCOMFORT: One of the biggest concerns with Fish Oil is the oil going rancid quickly, due to instability. The free fatty acid crystalline form of Omega 3 is perfectly stable - never going rancid & maintaining its full nutritional capacity. You won’t have to worry about the fish burps or stomach discomforts associated with fish oil. The fishy burps & stomach discomfort are because the oil requires intense digestion by the stomach.,MAXIMUM STRENGTH, EQUIVALENT TO 2250 mg OMEGA 3, EPA & DHA, BUT WITHOUT THE DISCOMFORT: Each serving provides 500 mg EPA & DHA in Free Fatty Acid form. Based on omega 3 performance this is equivalent to 2250 mg of standard fish oil*; plus you don't have to deal with the stomach discomfort and gross burps from taking a mega dose of fish oil. SoActive Omega 3 is the most effective performing omega 3 available.,CLEAN FORMULA YOU CAN TRUST, 3RD PARTY TESTED, MADE IN USA: This GMO-Free, Soy-Free & Gluten-Free formula is produced in an organic certified facility following all GMP standards. All ingredients are 3rd party tested and lab verified. The facility is FDA inspected – allowing you to rest assured your only taking the best. All Triquetra products are manufactured in the USA.

feature_bullets: DESIGNED FOR ATHLETES AND ACTIVE WARRIORS - Help support your body's recovery process after exercise with more DHA formulated in each softgel of iwi life Omega 3 Sport. Whether you're an athlete or just an active individual, this Omega-3 Sport supplement will help you live your best iwi life.,HIGHER DHA to SUPPORT MUSCLE RECOVERY - Sport is targeted to support post-workout recovery, joint function, heart health and mobility. And iwi life's nutrient-dense Vegan Omega-3 DHA formula is sustainably sourced from algae and formulated to benefit your overall health. These fatty acids strengthen nerve-cell membranes, helping maintain a sharp brain-body connection.,FACT: FISH and KRILL DON'T MAKE OMEGA-3s - they get them from algae. Athletes and active people know the importance of getting the right nutrition. Taking fish or krill oil to get your Omegas is like eating a steak to get your vegetables. Our sustainable, superior algae supplements provide true Omega-3 DHA. So, skip the "middle fish" and support your muscles, joints and heart better with iwi life.,TWO CAPSULES PER DAY FOR ULTIMATE RECOVERY SUPPORT - Each bottle of iwi life Sport delivers 60 softgels that contain no sugar, gelatin, nuts, or salt. No hidden additives, artificial colors or flavors. Gluten-free. The daily serving contains 950 mg of Algae Oil high in DHA Omega-3.,ABOUT IWI LIFE - Is dedicated to unlocking the secrets of Algae as a Superfood to bring you the ultimate in Earth-friendly plant-based vegan nutrition. We sun-grow our proprietary patented AlmegaPL algae right in the USA deserts of Texas and New Mexico, which is why you'll find Chlorophyll in our formula and you won't in others.
